OL,3,CCharity's pay offer 'just intolerable'
OL,4,Cclaim workers as strike action begins
OL,6,FStaff at one of the oldest and biggest
OL,7,Fmental health and housing charities in
OL,8,Fthe region have begun a seven-day
OL,9,Fstrike over pay.
OL,11,FWorkers at Second Step, which delivers
OL,12,Flocal authority and NHS-funded
OL,13,Fservices, took to a picket line
OL,14,Foutside the headquarters of Second
OL,15,FStep in Bristol.
OL,17,FIt's the latest move in a long-running
OL,18,Fprotest over what employees say is a
OL,19,Fbelow inflation pay offer.
