OL,3,CCharity's pay offer 'just intolerable'
OL,4,Cclaim workers as strike action begins
OL,6,FThe charity says offering more money
OL,7,Fto staff would put its services at
OL,8,F"unacceptable risk".
OL,10,FEmployee Mary Davies, who is based in
OL,11,FSomerset, told ITV News: "We work with
OL,12,Fpeople with complex needs. People need
OL,13,Fus and we don't want to strike.
OL,15,F"We're passionate and we do the job
OL,16,Fbecause we're certain people but,
OL,17,Fplease, don't take advantage of us
OL,18,Fbecause we do a good job. All we're
OL,19,Fasking for is to get the pay for what
OL,20,Fwe are doing."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
