OL,3,CCharity's pay offer 'just intolerable'
OL,4,Cclaim workers as strike action begins
OL,6,F"Retention is such a problem in this
OL,7,Fsector and that causes so much
OL,8,Fdisruption for people we support so
OL,9,Fpaying us better and keeping us in
OL,10,Fjobs is much better for everyone."
OL,12,FWorking across Wiltshire, Bath,
OL,13,FBristol, South Gloucestershire and
OL,14,FSomerset, Second Step has been
OL,15,Fsupporting thousands of people for
OL,16,Fnearly 40 years with issues such as
OL,17,Fhomelessness, mental health problems
OL,18,Fand recovery both in the community and
OL,19,Fin individuals' homes.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
