OL,3,CCharity's pay offer 'just intolerable'
OL,4,Cclaim workers as strike action begins
OL,6,FSecond Step say the strike action
OL,7,Fcomes despite talks with the union
OL,8,FUNISON and negotiators Acas.
OL,10,FIn a statement they said: "We cannot
OL,11,Foffer any uplift for the financial
OL,12,Fyear 2025/2026 as this would put our
OL,13,Fservice delivery at unacceptable risk
OL,14,Fand is not sustainable.
OL,16,F"We have made our tight financial
OL,17,Fsituation clear to UNISON at every
OL,18,Fstage of our negotiations.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
