OL,6,F"While we respect the right of union
OL,7,Fmembers to take lawful industrial
OL,8,Faction, our focus remains on
OL,9,Fmaintaining safe, continuous support
OL,10,Ffor the people who rely on our
OL,11,Fservices every day.
OL,13,F"We are working with our teams to put
OL,14,Four updated business continuity plans
OL,15,Finto action. Team managers and senior
OL,16,Fleaders are supporting colleagues to
OL,17,Fmake sure we minimise disruption."
